{"TopicId":210261,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"VAB Move Tool","CreatedByName":"capybara","CreatedById":212563,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-25T07:34:38Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"capybara","CreatedById":212563,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-25T07:34:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there any mod that lets you freely move objects in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, whenever i try move stuff too far it glitches out and stops me or just move it really close or up and down ect\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SSTO Crasher","CreatedById":215483,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-27T11:30:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u2019s not a glitch, there is a limiter on how far you can can offset it, you can deal with this by holding shift when using the offset tool\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-10-27T15:55:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224191589\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022210261\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221666870220\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022215483\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SSTO Crasher\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E Crasher said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nholding shift when using the offset tool\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt has a limit of 20 meters. However this limit can be changed in settings.cfg \u003Cspan\u003E:\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003EVAB_FINE_OFFSET_THRESHOLD = 20\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChange the 20 in whatever you want (for me it\u0027s 6433832).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}